---
// ComplianceSystemCTA — end-of-essay CTA block for compliance-tagged posts.
// Routes readers from the essay into the working compliance system:
// guide, assessment, and reference.
---

<aside class="compliance-cta" aria-label="Continue through the compliance system">
  <h3 class="compliance-cta-heading">Continue through the compliance system</h3>
  <p class="compliance-cta-body">
    LatentMesh organizes AI compliance as a practical loop: obligation, control,
    evaluation, evidence, and response. These links take you from the essay into
    the working system.
  </p>
  <div class="compliance-cta-links">
    <a href="/ai-compliance/" class="compliance-cta-link">
      <span class="compliance-cta-link-title">Start with the AI Compliance guide</span>
      <span class="compliance-cta-link-desc">The full operating model for production AI compliance.</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/tools/eu-ai-compliance-checker/" class="compliance-cta-link">
      <span class="compliance-cta-link-title">Assess your system</span>
      <span class="compliance-cta-link-desc">Use the EU AI Compliance Checker to understand your risk posture.</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/reference/eu-ai-act-controls/" class="compliance-cta-link">
      <span class="compliance-cta-link-title">Use the controls reference</span>
      <span class="compliance-cta-link-desc">Obligation-to-control mapping table for implementation.</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .compliance-cta {
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.65rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .compliance-cta-heading {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .compliance-cta-body {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .compliance-cta-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .compliance-cta-link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .compliance-cta-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-link);
  }

  .compliance-cta-link-title {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .compliance-cta-link-desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
